Grace was quiet...sweet...a seemingly gentle flower. Boy did she have everyone fooled!! Inside the petite lovely figure was a force to be reckoned with! Her quiet strength was just what Ryker Jensen needed! His seemingly narcissistic behavior melts with her humble presence in his life! And secrets left under wrap...reappear. Provocation is an action that demands a reaction....and Grace is full of it! Is she ready for the reaction she invokes in Ryker? "Provocation" is a story of new love and emotional reckoning! A push and pull of trust and hope!